    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable, java.lang.AutoCloseable
    public class Elevator
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Subsystem
    The elevator subsystem controls the elevator height with talon hardware PID. Contains methods for converting from encoder units to height, and vice versa too!
